{"tid":1257436,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵周日起加價 八達通新收費明年4月生效","createTime":"2019-06-25T14:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T14:20:48.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b3669ac8bd973986b30041fa74be0098a347ea85","tid":1257436,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190625/59756455?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Pg8qHVBpWqK_ub8LqmCUg_D1k2kk62fUlfCeHB3Po6tDzAzBeWS0_-bY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190625%2F59756455%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Pg8qHVBpWqK_ub8LqmCUg_D1k2kk62fUlfCeHB3Po6tDzAzBeWS0_-bY&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDs04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=60ac2944\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190625%2F59756455%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Pg8qHVBpWqK_ub8LqmCUg_D1k2kk62fUlfCeHB3Po6tDzAzBeWS0_-bY&h=4d88b74c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190625/59756455?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Pg8qHVBpWqK_ub8LqmCUg_D1k2kk62fUlfCeHB3Po6tDzAzBeWS0_-bY</a><br />\n<br />\n曾發生「四綫齊冧」及撞車等連串嚴重事故的港鐵，仍按可加可減機制加價3.3%，新票價將於本周日（30日）起生效。至於港鐵早前宣佈推出八達通每程扣減3.3%車費優惠，其優惠期至明年4月4日，為期40個星期。但加價之後，使用八達通的乘客於明年4月初才會有實質車費上調。<br />\n<br />\n另外，現時的「早晨折扣優惠」則延至明年5月31日，有關的折扣優惠亦會在10月由75折增至65折，覆蓋車站將由35個增至44個。而「全月通加強版」、「港鐵都會票」及「屯門-南昌全日通」等7款車票售價將維持至明年4月初。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人表示，各項計劃可為乘客節省合共逾8億元車費，連同港鐵每年27億元恆常優惠，於未來12個月將回饋逾35億元予乘客。"},{"pid":"f7678ba2cb579489bf032dc92201bb807780c8be","tid":1257436,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}